## Testing

```bash
cargo test --workspace -- --test-threads=1                      # All tests (always single-threaded)
cargo test --workspace storage -- --test-threads=1              # Module-specific
cargo test --workspace -- --test-threads=1 --nocapture          # With stdout
RUST_LOG=debug cargo test --workspace -- --test-threads=1 --nocapture  # With debug logging
cargo test --workspace test_name -- --exact --test-threads=1    # Single test by name
```

### Test conventions

- Every test gets its own `TempDir` → `KnowledgeGraph::new(temp_dir.path())`.
- No model downloads in unit tests. Embedding tests use `MockEmbeddingProvider`
  (deterministic fake vectors, defined inline) or skip when no Lemonade Server is
  reachable (auto-probed via `test_helpers::lemonade_url`).
- Transcription tests use `MockTranscriptionProvider` (returns a fixed string) for
  unit tests, or skip when no server is reachable for integration tests.
- Audio bytes in integration tests are generated by `make_silence_wav(secs)` — a
  pure-Rust WAV builder in the `embeddings` test module. No binary fixture files.
- Schema tests use `TempDir` for storage isolation.
- FTS5 search tests: insert a chunk, call `search_chunks_fts`, assert result.

### CI commands

```bash
cargo fmt --check
cargo clippy --workspace -- -D warnings
cargo test --workspace -- --test-threads=1
cargo doc --no-deps --workspace
cargo run --manifest-path crates/u-forge-core/Cargo.toml --example cli_demo
```

